category: Lua Database
requires: cygwin lua libopenldap2_3_0
sdesc: "Lua OpenLDAP bindings"
ldesc: "LuaLDAP is a simple interface from Lua to an LDAP client, in 
fact it is a bind to OpenLDAP or to ADSI. It enables a Lua program to:
* Connect to an LDAP server;
* Execute any operation (search, add, compare, delete, modify and rename);
* Retrieve entries and references of the search result."
